    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-07-18T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-07-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="1182"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1182">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Romero</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Day</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexican Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Atlantic City, N. J.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-07-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 18, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 2.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. Secretary</hi>: To-day I received your esteemed
                    circular communication dated the 15th of this month, in reference to the rules
                    which should be observed by war vessels of neutral nations entering or leaving
                    ports of Cuba and Porto Rico blockaded by the United States, and particularly
                    with reference to Habana, as also respecting any other ports which the United
                    States may in the future blockade during the war with Spain.</p>
                <p>In informing you that I have already transmitted a copy of this circular note to
                    my Government, I am pleased to reiterate, etc.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">M. Romero.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
